				<p><p>Basically it does not matter. <br>
But you have to be carefull if the plate is rotating fast, because the rotation of the plate around its center point, with the IMU placed out of center, will cause the accelerometer to measure centrifugal forces.</p>

<p>If your task is to stabalize the platform, this won't be an issue for you.</p>
